  "title": "Junior Sales Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<p>Our client is a leading top global bank seeking professional to drive business growth and build strong relationships with high-net-worth clients. You'll design and deliver customized investment solutions that address the complex needs of affluent individuals, helping them protect their assets and secure their financial future.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>- Assist the sales team in managing client relationships and meeting sales targets</p>\n<p>- Build and maintain relationships with clients, providing excellent customer service</p>\n<p>- Monitor and report on sales performance and identifying areas for improvement</p>\n<p>- Maintain knowledge of products and services, providing accurate information to clients</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>- Strong communication and interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>- Ability to work independently and as part of a team</p>\n<p>- Bachelor's degree, Local Diploma</p>\n<p><strong>What to Expect:</strong></p>\n<p>- Comprehensive training programs, mentorship</p>\n<p>- Opportunities for professional growth and development</p>\n<p>- Central work location</p>",
